meta {
  name: Get All Products
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&limit=50
  body: none
  auth: none
}

params:query {
  page: 1
  limit: 50
  ~category: Electronics
  ~is_active: true
  ~search: laptop
}

headers {
  Cookie: token={{token}}
  X-Organization-ID: {{orgId}}
}

docs {
  # Get All Products
  
  Lists all products within the organization.
  
  ## Authentication Required
  - HTTP-only cookie with access token (automatically sent)
  - **X-Organization-ID** header (required for organization context)
  
  ## Headers
  ```
  X-Organization-ID: 2
  ```
  
  ## Query Parameters
  - **page**: Page number (default: 1)
  - **limit**: Records per page (default: 50)
  - **category**: Filter by category
  - **is_active**: Filter active/inactive products
  - **search**: Search by name, SKU, or barcode
  - **min_price**: Minimum price filter
  - **max_price**: Maximum price filter
  - **low_stock**: true (show only low stock products)
  
  ## Response
  Returns paginated list of products from the specified organization only.
  
  ## Security
  - Backend validates user has access to organization
  - Products are scoped to organization ID
  - No cross-organization data access possible
}
